[05/02/2019 01:10:11] <font color="#ffffff">Bueno, sea.</font>
[05/02/2019 01:10:13] <font color="#ffffff">Recibamos esos tiros</font>
[05/02/2019 01:10:13] <font color="#ffffff">a bocajarro, seamos radicales</font>
[05/02/2019 01:10:16] <font color="#ffffff">y digamos que es mentira.</font>
[05/02/2019 01:10:18] <font color="#ffffff">¿Usted no se considera radical?</font>
